The paper deals with image synthesis using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The proposed method involves attention mechanisms and self-supervision, which are common techniques used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) research. The paper also mentions the use of large-scale datasets, which could fall under the graphics (cs.GR) category. Finally, the paper deals with image manipulation, which could also fall under the multimedia (cs.MM) category.
